1
00:00:06,940 --> 00:00:08,279
Miss Lin.

2
00:00:08,280 --> 00:00:09,440
(Chinese Textbook)

3
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:11,539
Why are you here?

4
00:00:11,540 --> 00:00:13,140
Is Shen Gu busy?

5
00:00:17,180 --> 00:00:18,499
Mr. Shen isn't busy.

6
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,460
He's waiting outside.

7
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:24,619
Did he ask you to pass me a message?

8
00:00:24,620 --> 00:00:26,539
Mr. Shen said you're upset.

9
00:00:26,540 --> 00:00:28,699
He'll wait until you calm down.

10
00:00:28,700 --> 00:00:30,619
What do you mean by I'm upset?

11
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:32,139
If he wants to wait, let him wait.

12
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:32,979
He's really

13
00:00:32,980 --> 00:00:34,939
stubborn and won't say a word.

14
00:00:34,940 --> 00:00:35,699
Exactly.

15
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:37,940
Why can't he say it face-to-face?

16
00:00:38,380 --> 00:00:40,220
Don't learn from him.

17
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:41,700
Bring him in.

18
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:42,979
Tell him to say

19
00:00:42,980 --> 00:00:44,379
what's in that letter himself.

20
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:45,499
Alright.

21
00:00:45,500 --> 00:00:46,620
Go on.

22
00:00:50,340 --> 00:00:51,299
Sir,

23
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:52,979
Miss Lin wants you to tell her

24
00:00:52,980 --> 00:00:54,660
what's written in the letter in person.

25
00:01:02,180 --> 00:01:04,460
Grandfather, let's go.

26
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:14,879
=Echoes of Gang City=

27
00:01:14,880 --> 00:01:19,200
=Episode 14=
(Today's pH Value &lt;7)

28
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:24,860
Wanxin wouldn't let me in just now.

29
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:28,940
Shen Gu wouldn't let me
get on the plane.

30
00:01:31,620 --> 00:01:33,860
I was worried you'd disturb Grandfather.

31
00:01:36,380 --> 00:01:38,060
Seriously, I'm really curious.

32
00:01:38,780 --> 00:01:40,060
What are you so happy about?

33
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:41,500
She didn't even let you in.

34
00:01:42,540 --> 00:01:43,980
Because she's angry.

35
00:01:44,740 --> 00:01:45,619
So?

36
00:01:45,620 --> 00:01:47,500
Do you know what that means?

37
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,660
She's jealous.

38
00:01:56,460 --> 00:01:57,660
She cares about me.

39
00:02:02,220 --> 00:02:03,340
Nice.

40
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:05,660
Love has finally taken over your brain,

41
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:06,900
you idiot.

42
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:10,540
I don't mean to rain on your parade.

43
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,140
There are a lot of eyes on us right now.

44
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:16,100
We need to solve the problem.

45
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:21,659
If this happens once,
it'll happen again.

46
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:23,100
We must nip it in the bud.

47
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:26,060
I'll call Su Mei
and have her come to Gang City.

48
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:27,860
Mr. Gu,

49
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:29,460
leave Su Mei

50
00:02:29,740 --> 00:02:30,860
to me.

51
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:33,660
Alright.

52
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:40,060
Su Mei has done too much
for you and Wanxin.

53
00:02:40,540 --> 00:02:42,100
Aren't you going to show
some appreciation?

54
00:02:44,260 --> 00:02:46,260
What do you want? Just say it.

55
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:51,939
Invite Ms. Su Mei to Gang City
to film Minghui's advertisement.

56
00:02:51,940 --> 00:02:53,939
Private jet pickup,
full production support,

57
00:02:53,940 --> 00:02:56,139
priority access throughout,

58
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:59,460
and global rollout
across six major social platforms.

59
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:01,580
That's the plan.

60
00:03:06,660 --> 00:03:08,260
You're just as crazy as I am.

61
00:03:10,620 --> 00:03:11,860
Takes one to know one.

62
00:03:12,540 --> 00:03:14,940
Why aren't you calling her yet?

63
00:03:18,740 --> 00:03:20,180
I need to freshen up

64
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:21,700
before I call her.

65
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:27,660
Hmm.

66
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,900
You're always the best.

67
00:03:32,180 --> 00:03:34,739
Did Shen Gu explain things to you?

68
00:03:34,740 --> 00:03:36,739
Why would he explain anything to me?

69
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:39,859
We're in a contract marriage.
It's a business arrangement.

70
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:42,139
What right do I have to ask?

71
00:03:42,140 --> 00:03:43,980
I'm not a real Mrs. Shen.

72
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:47,540
Xu Wanxin, you're done.

73
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:49,740
What's wrong with me?

74
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:54,660
You've started thinking about Mrs. Shen.

75
00:03:57,180 --> 00:04:00,740
Song Xixi, stop talking nonsense.

76
00:04:03,460 --> 00:04:04,339
My phone.

77
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:05,460
My phone's ringing.

78
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:09,660
- Who's calling this late?
- Xueli.

79
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:12,339
Hello?

80
00:04:12,340 --> 00:04:13,979
Ms. Song, we received
some insider gossip

81
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:16,979
about Ms. Wanxin and Mr. Shen.

82
00:04:16,980 --> 00:04:18,419
We can hold it back on our side,

83
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:21,540
but other outlets might not.

84
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:23,780
You may want to take a look first.

85
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,060
Alright.

86
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,940
What's wrong?

87
00:04:28,380 --> 00:04:30,180
What's with your face?

88
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,920
(International Star Su Mei
spotted with her lover late at night)

89
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:43,500
Nothing. Just scandals.

90
00:04:44,340 --> 00:04:45,780
Don't overthink it.

91
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:00,060
The attention is still increasing.

92
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:01,939
Should we clarify now and kill the buzz?

93
00:05:01,940 --> 00:05:03,380
I'll publish a demand letter now.

94
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,979
Clarification and demand letter

95
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:09,660
will only make it look like a cover-up.

96
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:12,779
But this is clearly targeting you.

97
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,580
It's dragging Su Mei into it now.

98
00:05:16,820 --> 00:05:19,059
Track Su Mei's schedule first.

99
00:05:19,060 --> 00:05:21,660
Let the trolls talk whatever they want.

100
00:05:21,860 --> 00:05:24,579
Let Shen Tingyuan drive the buzz
to its peak.

101
00:05:24,580 --> 00:05:27,660
Then flip the narrative
with Su Mei's arrival.

102
00:05:29,660 --> 00:05:30,780
That's the smarter move.

103
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:36,100
Reading

104
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,980
really helps.

105
00:05:41,620 --> 00:05:42,939
Whether it's true or not,

106
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:45,019
all we need to do is spread the rumors.

107
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:47,180
Xu Wanxin will believe it eventually.

108
00:05:47,740 --> 00:05:49,700
Once they get a divorce,

109
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:51,700
we'll have the upper hand

110
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:53,780
at the shareholders' meeting.

111
00:05:54,140 --> 00:05:56,060
Instead of these petty tricks,

112
00:05:56,700 --> 00:05:59,139
you'd be better off

113
00:05:59,140 --> 00:06:00,900
reaching out to more shareholders.

114
00:06:03,180 --> 00:06:03,980
Dad,

115
00:06:04,420 --> 00:06:05,540
don't worry.

116
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,460
This is just the beginning.

117
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:11,900
What Shen Gu and Xu Wanxin will face

118
00:06:12,460 --> 00:06:14,580
is far worse than this.

119
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:19,560
Shen Tingyuan has sent
a legal consultant to the company

120
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,300
to discuss terminating our cooperation.

121
00:06:22,260 --> 00:06:25,700
Just follow the proper procedures.

122
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,419
As for the scandal
about Shen Gu and Su Mei...

123
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:31,459
The tabloids in Gang City

124
00:06:31,460 --> 00:06:33,819
twist lies into truth.

125
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:37,660
They're sensational, vulgar,
and will target anyone.

126
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:40,539
There's no credibility left.

127
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:43,900
For any false reports
involving Wanxin and Shen Gu,

128
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,659
have legal handle them.

129
00:06:45,660 --> 00:06:47,419
Don't let a single one slip.

130
00:06:47,420 --> 00:06:48,540
Understood.

131
00:06:48,620 --> 00:06:50,939
But that won't have an immediate effect.

132
00:06:50,940 --> 00:06:53,380
I'll discuss a PR plan with them.

133
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:57,660
I'm sorry, Grandfather.

134
00:06:58,140 --> 00:07:01,580
I should've told you
about Shen Gu earlier.

135
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:03,140
It's fine.

136
00:07:03,780 --> 00:07:08,460
It's only a matter of time to end
cooperation between Minghui and Junlin.

137
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:12,379
Shen Gu is just an excuse.

138
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:15,579
Junlin is having
a shareholders' meeting soon.

139
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:17,819
Shen Tingyuan will do everything

140
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:20,300
to weaken Shen Gu's support.

141
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:25,340
The public is focused on your marriage.

142
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,900
How do you plan to respond?

143
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,700
Grandfather,

144
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:34,460
I...

145
00:07:35,460 --> 00:07:36,580
Wanxin,

146
00:07:37,140 --> 00:07:39,460
you don't need to consider anyone else.

147
00:07:39,540 --> 00:07:41,979
Your feelings matter most.

148
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:44,539
No matter what happens
between you and Shen Gu,

149
00:07:44,540 --> 00:07:47,300
I'll stand by you.

150
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:51,460
I won't let my granddaughter
suffer the slightest wrong.

151
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:54,100
Grandfather,

152
00:07:54,180 --> 00:07:57,100
Shen Gu helped us through our crisis
without hesitation.

153
00:07:57,340 --> 00:07:59,260
Now that he's in trouble,

154
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,580
with or without Su Mei,

155
00:08:01,660 --> 00:08:02,780
I won't leave him

156
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:05,580
at a time like this.

157
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:08,539
But people are saying
your marriage is just for show.

158
00:08:08,540 --> 00:08:10,700
There's a reason for that.

159
00:08:11,420 --> 00:08:13,580
You're married,

160
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:15,539
but you're still living here

161
00:08:15,540 --> 00:08:17,459
with me.

162
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:20,139
Grandfather, are you trying
to drive me away?

163
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:21,379
I just think

164
00:08:21,380 --> 00:08:24,700
I'm getting in the way of you two.

165
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:26,860
Of course not.

166
00:08:27,180 --> 00:08:28,739
But the way things are now,

167
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:31,659
it only fuels

168
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:34,860
speculations.

169
00:08:35,340 --> 00:08:36,339
What should I do?

170
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:37,819
Hold a press conference

171
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:40,139
and tell everyone we're in love?

172
00:08:40,140 --> 00:08:42,939
The more you explain,
the weaker it sounds.

173
00:08:42,940 --> 00:08:44,660
What can I do then?

174
00:08:45,540 --> 00:08:47,180
I think you're right.

175
00:08:50,020 --> 00:08:52,060
We should live together.

176
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:13,260
Why are you here?

177
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:39,459
We...

178
00:09:39,460 --> 00:09:40,299
Boss,

179
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:42,300
I'll put Miss Xu's luggage in your room.

180
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:45,420
Sorry.

181
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:46,940
We're staying separately.

182
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:54,259
You can take care of something else.

183
00:09:54,260 --> 00:09:55,380
I'll handle this.

184
00:10:14,860 --> 00:10:17,129
If there's anything you don't like,

185
00:10:17,130 --> 00:10:20,060
feel free to change it.

186
00:10:20,180 --> 00:10:21,260
It's fine.

187
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:24,620
Anyway, I'm only staying for a while.

188
00:10:26,100 --> 00:10:27,300
The news isn't true.

189
00:10:28,020 --> 00:10:30,059
There's nothing between Su Mei and me.

190
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:31,060
Shen Gu,

191
00:10:31,220 --> 00:10:33,500
you don't need
to explain anything to me.

192
00:10:34,300 --> 00:10:36,420
This is a contract marriage.

193
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:39,700
We don't interfere
in each other's feelings.

194
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:42,579
My only request is

195
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:44,900
that before we divorce,

196
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:46,780
you don't get involved
in any more scandals.

197
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,620
I don't want unnecessary trouble.

198
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:55,219
After your shareholders' meeting,

199
00:10:55,220 --> 00:10:56,620
we'll get divorced.

200
00:10:58,700 --> 00:11:00,100
We're not getting divorced.

201
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:18,460
Hello, Dai Anna.

202
00:11:18,540 --> 00:11:19,099
What's wrong?

203
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:19,899
Wanxin,

204
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:22,219
Shen Hao brought Wu Qing to the office.

205
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:24,299
They're asking to terminate
the endorsement deal.

206
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:25,659
Got it.

207
00:11:25,660 --> 00:11:26,900
I'm heading over now.

208
00:11:33,060 --> 00:11:34,620
I'll go with you.

209
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:43,180
There are paparazzi outside.

210
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:05,979
Move.

211
00:12:05,980 --> 00:12:08,339
Back off. Give them space.

212
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:09,899
Step back.

213
00:12:09,900 --> 00:12:10,740
Careful.

214
00:12:13,010 --> 00:12:14,619
Keep up.

215
00:12:14,620 --> 00:12:16,580
Let's go. Quick.

216
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:42,880
(Lawyer Fang: Su Mei has been picked up)

217
00:12:53,380 --> 00:12:54,580
Pour some water.

218
00:12:54,740 --> 00:12:55,820
There isn't any.

219
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:00,980
Ms. Wanxin.

220
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:04,940
You two are here.

221
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:08,219
You're impressive, Xu Wanxin.

222
00:13:08,220 --> 00:13:09,899
Such a huge scandal,

223
00:13:09,900 --> 00:13:11,460
and you act as if nothing happened.

224
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:16,380
Miss Wu,

225
00:13:17,180 --> 00:13:19,500
I was told
you want to terminate the contract.

226
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:24,340
I'm very sorry, Miss Xu.

227
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:26,380
It's a difficult situation for me.

228
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:29,619
The public sentiment around Minghui
hasn't been great lately.

229
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:32,420
Other brands are putting
a lot of pressure on me.

230
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,780
Miss Wu,

231
00:13:44,660 --> 00:13:46,300
Minghui has always given you

232
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:48,540
the best.

233
00:13:49,020 --> 00:13:51,620
There's no issue with our partnership.

234
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:54,300
If you terminate unilaterally,

235
00:13:54,580 --> 00:13:55,700
I think

236
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:59,220
it'll affect your future career.

237
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:02,300
Have you really thought this through?

238
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,139
Wanxin,

239
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:06,620
Wu Qing understands
Minghui's situation.

240
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,460
That's why she asked me to mediate.

241
00:14:08,860 --> 00:14:11,100
As long as Minghui Group

242
00:14:11,180 --> 00:14:14,580
can provide proof that you have
no connection with Shen Gu,

243
00:14:15,180 --> 00:14:16,780
she won't terminate.

244
00:14:17,260 --> 00:14:18,419
That way,

245
00:14:18,420 --> 00:14:20,900
she can explain to the other brands.

246
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:27,299
Anjie.

247
00:14:27,300 --> 00:14:28,059
Yes.

248
00:14:28,060 --> 00:14:31,140
Bring two termination agreements
from the legal department.

249
00:14:31,380 --> 00:14:32,900
We'll terminate now.

250
00:14:33,020 --> 00:14:34,140
Yes.

251
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:35,700
Xu Wanxin,

252
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:38,139
is it worth it

253
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,540
for a man who can't stay loyal?

254
00:14:39,820 --> 00:14:41,340
As long as you're willing,

255
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:43,219
Junlin Group and I will stand by you.

256
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:44,940
Don't you understand?

257
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:46,340
Shen Hao,

258
00:14:48,020 --> 00:14:49,180
mind your words.

259
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:52,579
An ambassador

260
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:54,699
who distances herself
and even throw us under the bus

261
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:56,900
the moment Minghui is in trouble,

262
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:59,780
we don't need that.

263
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:03,540
Miss Wu,

264
00:15:03,980 --> 00:15:06,300
thank you for your years
of work and support.

265
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:09,620
But ruining your future
for someone insincere

266
00:15:11,580 --> 00:15:13,020
isn't worth it.

267
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:18,300
I hope you make wiser choices
in the future

268
00:15:18,780 --> 00:15:20,020
and have a bright career ahead.

269
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:25,380
Fine.

270
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:28,380
A scandal-ridden man,

271
00:15:30,820 --> 00:15:32,420
and a hypocritical woman.

272
00:15:33,860 --> 00:15:35,900
Let's see how long
you two can keep this up.

273
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:38,180
Pay the penalty as soon as possible.

274
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:46,980
Your contract.

275
00:16:00,300 --> 00:16:02,740
If Wu Qing announces
the termination now,

276
00:16:02,900 --> 00:16:05,020
public sentiment against us
will only get worse.

277
00:16:06,060 --> 00:16:07,820
Where do we find a new ambassador?

278
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:13,499
The new ambassador

279
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,140
is on the way.

280
00:16:55,280 --> 00:17:01,080
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

281
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:08,160
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

282
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:14,240
♪You turn and look back at me♪

283
00:17:15,360 --> 00:17:20,880
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

284
00:17:21,720 --> 00:17:27,360
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

285
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:34,120
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

286
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:40,560
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

287
00:17:41,720 --> 00:17:47,520
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

288
00:17:47,920 --> 00:17:54,880
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

289
00:17:55,000 --> 00:18:00,680
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

290
00:18:01,360 --> 00:18:07,719
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

291
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:10,599
♪The promise we made♪

292
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:14,279
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

293
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:20,879
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

294
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:27,280
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

295
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:33,999
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

296
00:18:34,000 --> 00:18:39,120
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

297
00:18:39,600 --> 00:18:42,600
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
